body: Was out of the game for some time due to a Skype Virus sending all contacts messages with links in them that look completely innocent, it is a Google link with your Skype name in it, its a Trojan virus in total, it puts a key logger on your computer and yea... its kinda shit, but i got it off just now, just in the nick of time before it could do some permanent damage. If you guys have this type of virus, don't hesitate to contact me in the forum post, i know well how to deal with these now.
